SUMMARY:Deadline: Letters to Strangers Mental Health Scholarship 2026
DESCRIPTION:The Letters to Strangers Mental Health Scholarship supports stu
 dents and mental health advocates passionate about mental health awareness
 \, advocacy\, and creating positive change in their communities. The award
  is worth up to USD 8\,000 toward education. Apply via the Google Form lin
 ked below. Deadline 30 June 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Letters to Strangers\nL
 ocation: Open to students and mental health advocates passionate about men
 tal health awareness\, advocacy\, and creating positive change in their co
 mmunities.\nAward: Up to USD 8\,000 toward education.\nDuration: One-off s
 cholarship.\n\nMore: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScf0uJR32jmP
 QvHtJBAPdp_yd2nJFv1EbYtnfpj08nrQKeU_Q/viewform
URL:https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScf0uJR32jmPQvHtJBAPdp_yd2nJFv
 1EbYtnfpj08nrQKeU_Q/viewform
LOCATION:Open to students and mental health advocates passionate about ment
 al health awareness\, advocacy\, and creating positive change in their com
 munities.
END:VEVENT
